交通局英文網站
Welcome to the English version website of the Department of Transportation (with affiliated offices), Taipei City Government!
To enrich the website content and make it more convenient for users to search for information, the websites of the Department and its affiliated offices have been integrated into one single website. 歡迎使用本局及所屬機關英文網站-「臺北市政府交通局英文網站」為提升網站內容資料豐富度及使用者查詢資料之便利性，本局及所屬機關英文網站已整合為單一網站


